# LocusBLEScanner

The following repository contains a BLE scanner for the Locus Positioning indoor positioning service. It can be used to perform a scan using an Android smartphone to BLE beacons, and position the smartphone in an indoor environment using the Locus Positioning calibration-free positioning algorithms. 

To use this application, and account is required on the service of Locus Positioning:

www.locuspositioning.com


